N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 138.3 - Execution of statement

State Regulations

Statements of freedom from viruses required by this Part
must be the statement of the chief horticultural inspector, by whatever name
known, of the country, province or State in which such shipment
originated. Notes
